<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个悟空都看着谛听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是真悟空！”一个悟空大叫，“对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我才是！”另一个悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你们谁是假悟空。”谛听说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我不会说出来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>假悟空和真悟空的法力一样高强。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我说出来，他会生气的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可能会毁了整个幽冥界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说得对。”一个悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我想的话，我可以毁了整个幽冥界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我可以毁了这里。”另一个悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！”前一个悟空大叫，“我才可以！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个悟空又打了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请停下！”阎王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不要再打了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个悟空停了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们去找如来佛祖。”谛听说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他能辨认出你们谁才是真悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他法力高强，可以打败假悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的！”一个悟空说道，“我们去见佛祖！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，当然。”另一个悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去有点儿担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你紧张了！”第一个悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你知道佛祖会看出你是假的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“才不是！”另一个悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他生气地挥舞着金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出去！”阎王大叫，“去别的地方打！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个悟空离开了幽冥界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在天上激烈地打斗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天空中风起云涌，电闪雷鸣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们就到了西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个门将冲出了雷音寺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上住手！”他对着两个悟空大喊道，“谁在那里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个悟空落在了门将面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将看上去很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空？”他说，“怎么有两个悟空？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我！”一个悟空说，“我要马上见佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个悟空挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果佛祖很忙的话，我们就下次再来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个悟空瞪了他一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我们不能等了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们进去吧！”门将说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进去后，不要再打了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个悟空向雷音寺里走去，另一个悟空却向后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要和我一起去！”第一个悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓着另一个悟空的手臂，把他拉进了雷音寺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在佛祖面前，第一个悟空行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个悟空犹豫了一下，也行了礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，佛祖。”第一个悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要你的帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你为什么在这里，悟空。”佛祖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又看了看另一个悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是假悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个悟空大吃一惊，消失不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖举起一个碗，然后把它扣在了桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，假悟空已经被我扣在这碗的下面了。”佛祖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖移开了碗，一只小猴子精躺在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空靠近了去看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是只猴子，后来成了精。”佛祖说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他想成为你，因为你很强大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“很多妖精都想成为我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空谢过了佛祖，然后飞回了普陀山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨认为悟空是时候该回去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看见唐僧一行人正在去往西天的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨告诉了唐僧打他的不是悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须让悟空和你们一起去西天。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，观音菩萨。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢，观音菩萨。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定会保护唐僧到达西天的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>